00:00:00.930 --> 00:00:04.170 align:middle line:10%
>> The spectacular first images
from the James Webb Space

00:00:04.170 --> 00:00:07.950 align:middle line:10%
Telescope are finally here,
and they do not disappoint.

00:00:07.950 --> 00:00:11.440 align:middle line:90%
What this means for the future.

00:00:11.440 --> 00:00:12.885 align:middle line:90%
